--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Version 4.1.13, 2026-05-04
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
- Docker development stack (PHP 8.2, MySQL 8, seeded admin + disk source).
- GitHub Actions: PHP lint matrix, PHPUnit, Playwright E2E, MkDocs Pages, tag releases.
